747-a78f-fff843540000</link><description>周二的事件发生之际，约旦河西岸的定居者暴力事件不断增加，并试图为未来的定居点清理土地，而英国和美国则分别以前所未有的行动制裁了四名以色列极端主义定居者</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 10:22:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-13/ty-article/.premium/defense-official-israeli-settlers-torched-car-tried-to-set-building-on-fire-in-west-bank/0000018d-a1d0-d747-a78f-fff843540000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队公布了在加沙南部爆炸中丧生的三名士兵的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-13/ty-article/israeli-army-names-three-soldiers-killed-in-explosion-in-southern-gaza/0000018d-a1ac-d92c-a9ed-ebfdf95b0000</link><description>营长内塔内尔·雅科夫·埃尔库比 (Netanel Yaacov Elkouby)，36 岁；亚伊尔·科恩 (Yair Cohen) 少校，30 岁；中士。 26 岁的齐夫·陈 (Ziv Chen) 在加沙地带担任预备役军人，在汗尤尼斯 (Khan Yunis) 附近的一座建筑物内爆炸装置爆炸时身亡</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 10:06:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-13/ty-article/israeli-army-names-three-soldiers-killed-in-explosion-in-southern-gaza/0000018d-a1ac-d92c-a9ed-ebfdf95b0000</guid></item><item><title>与哈马斯的战斗留下焦土：战争对以色列自然造成的沉重打击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-13/ty-article/.premium/battles-with-hamas-leave-scorched-land-the-wars-heavy-toll-on-israeli-nature/0000018d-a17d-d747-a78f-ff7dc2ed0000</link><description>当以色列军队准备在北部与真主党作战时，它以牺牲景观为代价为坦克开辟了新道路。南部与哈马斯的战斗导致多个自然保护区发生火灾，跨境流浪狗引发疾病流行的担忧</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 09:55:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-13/ty-article/.premium/battles-with-hamas-leave-scorched-land-the-wars-heavy-toll-on-israeli-nature/0000018d-a17d-d747-a78f-ff7dc2ed0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部男子被枪杀；二月阿拉伯以色列社会第九名凶杀案受害者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-13/ty-article/.premium/man-shot-dead-in-israels-north-ninth-homicide-victim-in-arab-israeli-society-in-february/0000018d-a168-d416-a3ed-edfa0f970000</link><description>纳比·塔巴拉尼 (Nabih Tabarani) 在该市的一处观景台附近被发现中弹，就在他正在行驶的车辆旁边。警方不认识他</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 08:03:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-13/ty-article/.premium/man-shot-dead-in-israels-north-ninth-homicide-victim-in-arab-israeli-society-in-february/0000018d-a168-d416-a3ed-edfa0f970000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布了哈马斯领导人辛瓦尔从战争开始时在加沙隧道的镜头</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-13/ty-article-live/israeli-delegation-to-attend-cairo-hostage-talks-on-tuesday-with-u-s-qatar-egypt/0000018d-a049-d92c-a9ed-ebf955ed0000</link><description>加沙报道：加沙城汽车袭击造成四人死亡 ■ 熟悉谈判的外国消息人士称，人质交易取得了一些进展 ■ 以色列国防军：以色列军队在昨天打死了 40 多名恐怖分子 ■ 三名利库德集团成员：我们呼吁内塔尼亚胡军事草案法案作为临时命令通过，有效期仅为一年 ■ 以色列准备在拉法进行全面行动，国际社会对以色列发出警告</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 02:39:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-13/ty-article-live/israeli-delegation-to-attend-cairo-hostage-talks-on-tuesday-with-u-s-qatar-egypt/0000018d-a049-d92c-a9ed-ebf955ed0000</guid></item><item><title>法国提议真主党撤军并就以黎停战进行边界谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-13/ty-article/france-proposes-hezbollah-withdrawal-border-talks-for-israel-lebanon-truce/0000018d-9fd4-d92c-a9ed-fffdc00b0001</link><description>该三步走计划设想为期 10 天的降级过程，以边界谈判结束；以色列官员称耶路撒冷正在评估该提案</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 00:50:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-13/ty-article/france-proposes-hezbollah-withdrawal-border-talks-for-israel-lebanon-truce/0000018d-9fd4-d92c-a9ed-fffdc00b0001</guid></item><item><title>令人印象深刻的以色列国防军救援行动证明内塔尼亚胡可以在他愿意的时候“承担责任”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-13/ty-article/.premium/impressive-idf-rescue-op-proves-that-netanyahu-can-take-responsibility-when-he-wants-to/0000018d-9ee3-d747-a78f-fefbcdd90000</link><description>在加沙地带南部的拉法，两名以色列人质被完美解救，这一切都归功于士兵和他们的指挥官。任何声称将以同样大胆的方式释放所有剩余人质的人都是在撒谎。这并非巧合，因为他们正是试图让我们相信没有机会达成另一项协议的人</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 00:16:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-13/ty-article/.premium/impressive-idf-rescue-op-proves-that-netanyahu-can-take-responsibility-when-he-wants-to/0000018d-9ee3-d747-a78f-fefbcdd90000</guid></item><item><title>英国工党与一名候选人断绝关系，该候选人称以色列允许哈马斯发动袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-02-13/ty-article/british-labour-party-cuts-ties-with-candidate-who-said-israel-allowed-oct-7-to-happen/0000018d-9f93-df62-a3fd-9f9f563c0001</link><description>爱资哈尔·阿里已为这些言论道歉，但被他的政党停职——该党仍在从前党魁杰里米·科尔宾领导下的制度性反犹太主义指控中恢复过来</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 00:02:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-02-13/ty-article/british-labour-party-cuts-ties-with-candidate-who-said-israel-allowed-oct-7-to-happen/0000018d-9f93-df62-a3fd-9f9f563c0001</guid></item></channel></rss>